# Unicode.GeneralCategory.otherPunctuation

**Case**

A punctuation mark of another type.

## Declaration

```swift
case otherPunctuation
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Other_Punctuation` (abbreviated `Po`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
